review_content:
from fall to spring: day/night fragrance;
summer: only night for me.
I've bought 200ml of this fragrance for only €29... the smell is AMAZING. Everyone loves it, no one can dislike it, only niche owner will snob it. Performance are not so great but you can spray it a lot (because the price is ridicolous) and going to smell it for 4-5 hours.
